                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18220109-130-off689 t18220109-130-cd690"></join>, 24 lbs. of lead, value 9 s., and one fixture, (i.e.) one brass cock, value 3 s., the goods of 
                     
